---
permalink: /blog/
layout : default
footerStyle: gray
excerpt: In unserem Blog teilen wir alles Relevante rund um die Themen Chatbot und Conversational AI.
---

<div class="blog-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p class="intro">In unserem Chatbot Blog teilen wir alles Relevante rund um die Themen
      <span>Chatbot</span>&nbsp;und&nbsp;<span>Conversational AI</span>.</p>
    <p class="social">
      <a
        class="button button-action"
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/bubble-chat"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Folgen Sie uns auf LinkedIn um nichts zu verpassen</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div style="background-color: #f5f5f7; padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <ul class="feature-cards">
        {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
          <li class="feature-cards__item">
            <a class="card" href="{{ post.url | url }}">
              {% if post.data.image %}
                <div class="header-img" style="background-image: url({% jpgUrl '/site' + post.data.image, 500 %}')"></div>
              {% else %}
                <div class="header-img" style="background-image: url({% jpgUrl '/img/og-image.png', 500 %}')"></div>
              {% endif %}
              <div class="card-content">
                <h3 class="card-title">
                  {% if post.data.displayTitle %}
                    {{ post.data.displayTitle | safe }}
                  {% else %}
                    {{ post.data.title }}
                  {% endif %}
                </h3>
                <div class="card-desc">
                  {{ post.data.excerpt |Â safe }}
                </div>
                <div class="card-actions">
                  <span class="btn btn-block">Mehr erfahren</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
